②A woman in a black dress is walking on the street;
③To the woman's rear-left, there is a person A in white shorts walking in the opposite direction.
④Person A has passed a person standing still.
What was this stationary person doing when person A passed them?

Find the only pedestrian in the frame who meets all the following criteria:
①Is male;
②Is wearing a short-sleeved shirt with at least two colors;
③Is wearing white shorts.
At the moment he is closest to the nearest lamppost, which store is he closest to?

