③A woman in a gray top with a white pattern is just about to disappear from the bottom left corner of the frame.
At this moment, has the man in the yellow T-shirt already passed the red postbox (assuming a line perpendicular to the street is drawn from the postbox as a boundary)?

Please find a group of three people in the video who simultaneously meet the following conditions:
①There are two women and one man;
②The man is wearing a black top and dark pants;
③One of the women is holding a bag;
④No one is wearing sunglasses.
What color is the woman's bag?

